\displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n^4}.
\displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n^4} = \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{(2n-1)^4} + \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{(2n)^4}.
\displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n^4} = \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{(2n-1)^4} + \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{(2n)^4} 
n
\displaystyle \frac{1}{n^4} = \frac{1}{(2n-1)^4} + \frac{1}{(2n)^4}
\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{1}{n^4}=\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{1}{(3n)^4}+\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{1}{(3n-1)^4}+\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{1}{(3n-2)^4}
m
\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{1}{n^4}=\sum_{k=0}^{m-1}\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{1}{(mn-k)^4}
